{"tid":1945091,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男警涉售冒牌波鞋抗海關執法 5月轉往觀塘法院再訊","createTime":"2020-03-26T23:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T23:52:51.000Z","uid":125193,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7213a1be1f8943a8c5b1fe778ac8a56477c52449","tid":1945091,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T23:27:00.000Z","msg":"被告黃港恆。<br />\n25歲男警涉於去年9月26日，在港鐵觀塘站出售Adidas的冒牌波鞋，又疑抗拒海關人員執法，事後被控出售應用偽造商標的貨品、管有應用偽造商標的貨品及抗拒海關人員等4罪。案件今在西九龍法院提訊，案件押後至5月25日轉往觀塘法院再訊。被告獲准以原有2000元保釋外出。<br />\n<br />\n25歲被告黃港恆報稱任職巡邏警員，出售應用偽造商標的貨品，及管有應用偽造商標的貨品兩罪指，被告於2019年9月26日在觀塘港鐵站大堂近A出口，出售一對偽造商標的貨品，即一對Adidas波鞋；及在同日同地管有兩對Adidas的冒牌球鞋。被告另被控2項抗拒海關人員罪，控罪指他於同日同地抗拒2名正當執行職務的海關人員。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>據了解，被告涉在二手網站出售冒版波鞋，最終海關人員趁他現身交收時拘捕他，期間懷疑反抗，致2名海關人員受傷。</strong><br />\n<br />\n被告今毋須答辯，裁判官應辯方申請將案件押後，以待索取文件及向被告提供法律意見。<br />\n<br />\n法庭記者：陳楚琨<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200325/bkn-20200325163536925-0325_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200325%2Fbkn-20200325163536925-0325_00822_001.html&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=41c40c03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200325/bkn-20200325163536925-0325_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1731525/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6%E6%B6%89%E5%94%AE%E5%86%92%E7%89%8C%E6%B3%A2%E9%9E%8B%E6%8A%97%E6%B5%B7%E9%97%9C%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95-5%E6%9C%88%E8%BD%89%E5%BE%80%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1731525%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%2594%25AE%25E5%2586%2592%25E7%2589%258C%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E9%259E%258B%25E6%258A%2597%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%259F%25B7%25E6%25B3%2595-5%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%25BD%2589%25E5%25BE%2580%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A8%258A&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=59ba995c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1731525%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%2594%25AE%25E5%2586%2592%25E7%2589%258C%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E9%259E%258B%25E6%258A%2597%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%259F%25B7%25E6%25B3%2595-5%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%25BD%2589%25E5%25BE%2580%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A8%258A&h=d3bc08ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1731525/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6%E6%B6%89%E5%94%AE%E5%86%92%E7%89%8C%E6%B3%A2%E9%9E%8B%E6%8A%97%E6%B5%B7%E9%97%9C%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95-5%E6%9C%88%E8%BD%89%E5%BE%80%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%8A</a>"},{"pid":"2de84c8c2439c112a91b325ee7f38a38b79c0edd","tid":1945091,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T23:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}